title: House for rent - Available in August

very open,', 'hardwood floor,', 'high-end appliances,', 'covered patio which you can enjoy all year round,', 'privet backyard with large trees surrounded by water ponds - Very Relaxing.', 'Main floor offers:', 'Large Living Room,', 'Family Room w/ Gas Fireplace,', 'Formal Dining Room,', 'huge Kitchen with high-end stainless appliances and a lot of cabinets,', '3/4 Guest Bath,', 'Laundry Room / Mud Room with storage cabinets and sink.', 'Upstairs includes:', 'Master Suite with walk-in cedar closet, 5-pc Master Bath w/ Tub.', 'Two large additional Bedrooms, Full Bath w/ double sinks.', 'Loft w/ built-in workspace for play area, crafts, or home office, new AC, 3-Car Garage (garage has office / storage area), humidifier, full house water filtering system, security system,', 'large room in the basement, perfect for storage or play room', 'Beautifully landscaped with large trees (semiprivate), surrounded by neighbors waterfalls which makes it very relaxing surrounding, fenced yard with organic vegetable and fruit garden.', 'Non-Smoking property.', 'Pets are negotiable case by case.', 'Additional and refundable Pet deposit = $1,500.', 'Max of dogs = 1', 'Please provide the pet breed, age, weight when you contact us.', 'Owner pays trash and water, refrigerator air and water filters, Ventilation filters.', 'Tenants pay electric, gas and internet or cable (if applies).', 'Short lease can be considered:', '6 month lease = $5,550 per month', '9 month lease = $4,850 per month', '12 month lease = $4,350 per month', 'Please email with questions', 'Thank you!']
